headline: 1 Software Stock to Target This Week and 2 to Avoid
summary: From commerce to culture, software is digitizing every aspect of our lives. The undeniable tailwinds fueling the industry have also led to strong returns for SaaS stocks lately as they’ve gained 7% over the past six months, outpacing the S&P 500’s 1.1% rise.
